# Workspace

- **Platform:** Panax (panax.ai) — owns all product apps and shared Postgres.
- **Products:** `sites/*` → `.ing` domains (powerlift, itrain.ing, …). **itrain.ing is one product**, not the platform.
- **Repo:** may live at `~/itrain.ing` or `~/panax` until [docs/RENAME.md](../docs/RENAME.md).
- **API host:** `api.panax.ai` (not `api.itrain.ing`).
- Micro-commits per [.cursor/rules/micro-commits.mdc](micro-commits.mdc). No agent git attribution.
